OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774505052
OL,3,CFarage to launch Reform local election
OL,4,Ccampaign promising 'breath of fresh
OL,5,Cair'
OL,7,FHe is expected to use the event to
OL,8,Flist a series of achievements in the
OL,9,Flocal authorities already run by
OL,10,FReform, saying voters were "already
OL,11,Fseeing a difference on the ground".
OL,13,FAhead of the rally, Mr Farage said
OL,14,FReform was "delivering a total culture
OL,15,Fshift in local government, sweeping
OL,16,Faway the establishment consensus and
OL,17,Ffinally putting residents first".
OL,26,@rD@\OUsD@bO]vD@LOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774505052
OL,3,CFarage to launch Reform local election
OL,4,Ccampaign promising 'breath of fresh
OL,5,Cair'
OL,7,FHe added: "Where the old parties have
OL,8,Ffailed and left behind a trail of
OL,9,Fruined councils in their wake, Reform
OL,10,Fwill deliver a breath of fresh air in
OL,11,FEnglish councils up and down the UK."
OL,13,FCentral to his pitch will be Reform's
OL,14,Fclaim to have identified #700 million
OL,15,Fin savings across its 12 councils,
OL,16,Fwhich Mr Farage claimed had been
OL,17,Fdelivered "without touching frontline
OL,18,Fservices".
OL,20,FIn November last year, Reform said its
OL,21,Fcouncils had saved #331 million.
OL,26,@oD@KOUsD@eO]yD@KOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
