FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774505052
OL,3,CFarage to launch Reform local election
OL,4,Ccampaign promising 'breath of fresh
OL,5,Cair'
OL,7,FReform continues to lead in the polls
OL,8,Fand is expected to do well in May,
OL,9,Fadding to the 677 councillors it won
OL,10,Fin last year's local elections.
OL,12,FBut its claims to have achieved
OL,13,Fsignificant savings have been disputed
OL,14,Fby opposition councillors, while
OL,15,FLabour has pointed to care homes and
OL,16,Fadult education services closing in
OL,17,FReform-run Derbyshire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774505052
OL,3,CFarage to launch Reform local election
OL,4,Ccampaign promising 'breath of fresh
OL,5,Cair'
OL,7,FLabour has also criticised Reform for
OL,8,Fincreasing council tax despite
OL,9,Fpromising to cut the levy before last
OL,10,Fyear's local elections.
OL,12,FReform now says council tax rises in
OL,13,Fauthorities where it has majority
OL,14,Fcontrol have averaged less than those
OL,15,Frun by Labour, the Conservatives or
OL,16,Fthe Lib Dems, while describing below-
OL,17,Finflation increases in some councils
OL,18,Fas a "real-terms tax cut".
OL,26,@zD@FOUzD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774505052
OL,3,CFarage to launch Reform local election
OL,4,Ccampaign promising 'breath of fresh
OL,5,Cair'
OL,7,FBut this does not include
OL,8,FWorcestershire, where Reform runs a
OL,9,Fminority administration and increased
OL,10,Fcouncil tax this year by 9%.
OL,12,FLabour Party chairwoman Anna Turley
OL,13,Fsaid: "Reform's promises fall apart
OL,14,Fthe moment they take power.
OL,16,F"They said they would cut taxes and
OL,17,Fwaste, but in council after council
OL,18,Fthey're hiking council tax and
OL,19,Fslashing services."
OL,26,@uD@GOUxD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
